we have craeted two folder 
Tanzo for frontend and contract for the blockchain part......

***********************
Tanzo Folder.....
***********************

**command to install the react js using vite, we are using vite cause it is fast for development......
npm create vite@latest
npm i //to install the dependencies

**we will use tailwind css for our frontend...**
npm install -D tailwindcss
npx tailwindcss init // this command will create a tailwind config file

**configure the tailwind file**
/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
module.exports = {
  content: ["./src/**/*.{html,js}"],
  theme: {
    extend: {},
  },
  plugins: [],
}

**paste the code in index.css**
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

**start the tailwind CLI build process**
npx tailwindcss -i ./src/input.css -o ./dist/output.css --watch

**Add the output file css to the App.jsx file**




